1 UI : I home page, user will see all drives
2 UI : No auth/user login required
3 UI : drive list will come from config/drives.json file
4 UI: When user click any drive then show list of contents of selectd drive
5 UI: User can click file to download this file
6 UI: Click folder to navigate folder, also user may download folder instead of default navigate (use zip)
7 UI: Show the current path on top bar (dont show default UI of serve-index)
8 UI: Show upload button (want to upload currrent path insted of uploads folder)


